rComments: Great prof. Always clear what he wants from day one. the class is boring by nature if you don't enjoy poetry but he makes it so much easier.

Anstee was a really great prof.  His lectures were always really interesting and he's very helpful.  His feedback on essays is really useful. He's also ridiculously attractive.  The only thing that I disliked about the class was the large focus on modernism (I would have liked to explore other subjects of English as well).

Awesome professor.  Kind person who loves English and the works he teaches.  Not an easy marker,  but a fair one who will give you extensions and such if you need them. It's refreshing to have a prof who wants you to succeed.

Super clear in what he wants for you. As someone not super into poetry, he managed to make calss super interresting and fun.  Really nice prof who clearly wants his students to do the best they can while still marking fairly.  If you show up to class, you get participation marks and learn a lot.

LOVE HIM! He made every class so interesting and was so enthusiastic about teaching and learning. He's always available for assistance, easily the most helpful prof I've had. And he really wants his students to succeed. Overall super genuine man. oh and he's unbelievably cute which is a huge bonus
Honestly worst prof Ive had so far.

You can tell he wants his students to succeed. He makes himself constantly available for anyone who needs his help. I would easily take his class again. Besides all that, the guy is a complete heart throb.

Cameron is a great teacher. This class was his first and he did exceptionally. He made every lesson interesting, and you can see his true passion for the subject matter. He always made himself available and was a great help with problem solving. Always willing to go the extra mile. ps he is extremely gorgeous, so that helped too ;)

Great prof! My class was the first he ever taught and he did an exceptional job. Super helpful with essays and extra help, clear, and he made poetry from the 1800s interesting! Definitely recommend him and his class. Such a hottie too
